# always-ingest-bootstrap

When the user says **"INGEST MODE"**, **"Process Ingest"**, or **"run ingests"**, ingest processing is handled by the **IngestSubagent** ([agents/ingest.mdc](.cursor/rules/agents/ingest.mdc)). That subagent runs non-MD handling, embedded image normalization, Phase 1 full-autonomous-ingest (propose + Decision Wrapper), and Phase 2 apply-mode when triggered by approved wrappers via EAT-QUEUE. No ingest logic here; routing is via system-funnels and dispatcher to IngestSubagent.
